---
title: Charred Barbecue Chicken with Black Bean & Corn Salad
description: Barbecue chicken and corn scream summer entertaining. No backyard party is complete without them! This salad is excellent served warm or cold—perfect for picnics. If you have a grill, feel free to cook the chicken and corn there!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/charred-barbecue-chicken-5a0101b9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/charred-barbecue-chicken-cea47aef.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/charred-barbecue-chicken-57558d5bfd2cb9fa538b4567
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
